<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | Atakan GÃ¼l's Blog</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/semantic-ui@2.4.2/dist/semantic.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap');
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8;
        }
        .custom-yellow {
            background-color: #ffc107;
        }
        .custom-yellow-text {
            color: #ffc107;
        }
        .icon-circle {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: white;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
       
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100">
    <% if (isAdmin) { %>  
        <%- include('../partials/headers/headerAdmin.ejs') %>
    <% } else if (isAuthenticated) { %>
        <%- include('../partials/headers/headerAuth.ejs') %>
    <% } else { %>
        <%- include('../partials/headers/headerUnAuth.ejs') %>
    <% } %>
    
    <header class="bg-white shadow-md">
        <nav class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">About</h1>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="container ui mx-auto px-4">
        <!-- Header Section -->
        <section class="text-center mb-12 py-16">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 custom-yellow-text">
                <i class="fas fa-laptop-code mr-3"></i>Welcome to The Tech Hub
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Exploring the frontiers of technology, one byte at a time.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- About Content -->
        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 mb-12 hover-grow">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="icon-circle mr-4"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i></span>
                About This Blog
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl mb-6">
                This blog is my digital playground where I explore and share insights about the ever-evolving world of technology. As a software developer with a passion for learning, I've created this space to:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-none text-xl space-y-4 mb-6">
                <li><i class="fas fa-share-alt text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Share knowledge and experiences in software development</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-microchip text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Discuss cutting-edge technologies and their impacts</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-book-open text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Provide practical tips and tutorials for fellow developers</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-brain text-yellow-500 mr-2"></i> Explore the intersection of AI, cloud computing, and web development</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-xl">
                Whether you're a seasoned developer or just starting your tech journey, I hope you'll find something valuable here. Let's learn, grow, and innovate together!
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Subscribe Section -->
        <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 hover-grow">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center">
                <span class="icon-circle mr-4"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></span>
                Stay in the Loop
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl mb-6">Want to keep up with the latest in tech? Subscribe for fresh insights delivered straight to your inbox!</p>
            <%- include('../partials/subscribe.ejs') %>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>